params.description: The setting that defines how metastore metadata should be integrated with external services and systems.

params.description: The one hour maintenance window of the metastore service. This specifies when the service can be restarted for maintenance purposes in UTC time. Maintenance window is not needed for services with the SPANNER database type.

params.description: Immutable. The configuration specifying the network settings for the Dataproc Metastore service.

params.name: data.database_type
params.description: Immutable. The database type that the Metastore service stores its data.
